function SndTest% SndTest alternately plays the same sound (someone saying "why") % with 8 or 16 bit encoding, to allow you the hear the difference, % which is a faint hiss produced by the coarse 8-bit quantization.% 1/8/00 Lu Lesmes, lesmes@usc.edu, wrote it.% 1/30/00 dgp cosmetic editing[y,rate,bits]=wavread('SndTest.wav');for i=1:4% 	sound(y,FS,16)	SND('Play',y',rate,16);	SND('Wait');%	sound(y,FS,8)	SND('Play',y',rate,8);	SND('Wait');end